title: Grateful Dead Live at Sam Boyd Silver Bowl, U.N.L.V. on 1995-05-21
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, West L.A. Fadeaway, Little Red Rooster, Ramble On Rose, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, So Many Roads, Promised Land

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Unbroken Chain, Eyes Of The World-> Corinna-> Drums*-> Space-> The Other One-> The Days Between-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Liberty

Other Artist(s): Dave Mathews Band openned. * w/ Carter Beauford of DMB
